msgid "Common Questions"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:209
msgid "Q: Why can't I see my address history?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:211
msgid ""
"**A:** Address history (verblijfplaatshistorie) is coming in a future "
"update. Currently, only person/partner/children data is shown."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:213
msgid "Q: Can I change my past data?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:215
msgid ""
"**A:** No, the timeline shows BRP data which is the official government "
"record. To correct errors, contact your municipality's BRPloket."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:217
msgid "Q: Why does it say I'm 0 years old?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:219
msgid ""
"**A:** You selected your birth date. At birth, age is 0. Move forward in "
"time to see your age increase."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:221
msgid "Q: Can I print or export my timeline?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:223
msgid "**A:** Not yet. Export to PDF is planned for a future release."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:225
msgid "Q: What are \"what if\" scenarios?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:227
msgid ""
"**A:** This is a future feature where you can simulate life changes (having "
"a child, getting divorced) to see how they affect your benefits eligibility."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:229
msgid "Q: Why do I only see one test person?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:231
msgid ""
"**A:** The test environment currently has one demo persona (Wessel Kooyman). "
"More diverse test data will be added."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:233
msgid "Q: How far into the future can I go?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Ctimeline-navigation.md:235
msgid ""
"**A:** You can select dates up to 10 years in the future for planning "
"purposes."
msgstr ""

